# FitMe AI — Cloud deploy (Vercel + Render + Neon)
# Copy sections below into each platform's dashboard. Do NOT commit real secrets.

# ── Neon (PostgreSQL) ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Create project at https://neon.tech → Connection string (direct, not pooled for Flyway)
# Example JDBC (append sslmode=require if missing):
# DB_URL=jdbc:postgresql://ep-xxxx.ap-southeast-1.aws.neon.tech/neondb?sslmode=require
# DB_USERNAME=neondb_owner
# DB_PASSWORD=your-neon-password

# ── Render (Spring Boot backend) ────────────────────────────
# Web Service → Docker → backend/Dockerfile
# DB_URL=
# DB_USERNAME=
# DB_PASSWORD=
# JWT_SECRET=random-string-min-32-chars
# CORS_ORIGINS=https://your-app.vercel.app
# FITME_SEED_ENABLED=true
# FITME_SEED_PASSWORD=fitme123
# UPLOAD_DIR=/tmp/uploads

# ── Vercel (Next.js frontend) ─────────────────────────────────
# Root Directory: frontend
# Framework: Next.js
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=/api/v1
# BACKEND_INTERNAL_URL=https://fitme-api.onrender.com
#   ↑ URL Render backend (no trailing slash), set AFTER first Render deploy
